{
  "texts": [
    "The proteomes were blasted against their respective databases (Protein-Protein BLAST 2.9.0+).",
    "Two sequences were considered homologous if the blast hit had an e-value <0.001 and a bit score >50.",
    "Genes in the validation chromosome that had homologous pairs in the training chromosomes were dropped.",
    "Convolutional neural networks were built using the sequential API of tensorflow-keras.",
    "All models had three convolutional blocks, each convolutional block had two convolutional layers followed by a max pooling and a dropout layer."
  ]
}